\c 7
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti Jehovha amururamisire
\p Shigayoni yaDhavhidhi yaakaimbira Jehovha pamashoko aKushi muBhenjamini.
\p
\v 1 Haiwa Jehovha Mwari wangu, ndinovimba nemi; ndiponesei kune vese vanonditeverera, mundinunure.
\v 2 Zvimwe abvambure mweya wangu seshumba, aubvamburanye pasina anorwira.
\v 3 Haiwa Jehovha Mwari wangu, kana ndakaita izvi; kana mune chakaipa mumaoko angu;
\v 4 kana ndakatsiva chakaipa kune waiva nerygare neni (koga ndakapamba ari muvengi wangu pasina chikonzero);
\v 5 muvengi ngaateverere mweya wangu, aubate; ngaatsikire-tsikire upenyu hwangu pasi, nerukudzo rwangu aise muguruva, Sera.
\p
\v 6 Mukai Jehovha, pakutsamwa kwenyu; zvisimudzei nekuda kwekutsamwa kwevavengi vangu, mukai nekuda kwangu, makaraira mutongo.
\v 7 Saizvozvo ungano yevendudzi ichakupoteredzai; nekuda kwavo dzokerai kumusoro pamusoro pavo.
\v 8 Jehovha anotonga ndudzi; nditongei, haiwa Jehovha, zvichienderana nekururama kwangu, uye zvichienderana neuchokwadi hwangu.
\v 9 Haiwa, kuipa kwevakaipa ngakugume, asi simbisai wakarurama; nokuti anoedza moyo netsvo ndiMwari wakarurama.
\p
\v 10 Nhovo yangu iri kuna Mwari, muponesi wevakarurama pamoyo.
\v 11 Mwari mutongi wakarurama, uye ndiMwari anotsamwira \add wakaipa\add* nguva dzese.
\p
\v 12 Kana asingatendeuki, acharodza munondo wake; wakunga uta hwake, ndokuhugadzirira.
\v 13 Wakamugadzirirawo nhumbi dzokuuraya nadzo; anoitira vadzingiriri miseve inopisa.
\v 14 Tarira, anotambudzika pakubereka zvakaipa; zvirokwazvo, akava nemimba yezvakashata, akabereka nhema.
\v 15 Akachera hunza, akaidzikisa, akawira mugomba raakachera iye.
\v 16 Zvakashata zvake zvichadzokera pamusoro wake amene, uye kumanikidza kwake kuchauya pamusoro panhongonya yake.
\p
\v 17 Ndichavonga Jehovha nokuda kokururama kwake; ndichaimbira zita raJehovha Wekumusoro-soro.
